node_7.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 9:00 am, go to Hobbs Cafe and have breakfast at 10:00 am, get to Twitch Studio and start streaming/gaming from 11:00 am to 2:00 pm, take a lunch break and have lunch at Hobbs Cafe at 2:00 pm, resume gaming/streaming from 3:00 pm to 6:00 pm, have dinner and take a break at Hobbs Cafe at 7:00 pm.
